{"data": [{"id": "4743222", "title": "Putting Rivian Automotive's Latest Surge In Perspective", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rivian R1S EV Electric Vehicle display at a dealership. Rivian offers the R1S in Adventure and Launch models.\" data-id=\"1488373216\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>December 9th ended up being a really positive day for shareholders of electric vehicle producer <strong>Rivian Automotive</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RIVN\" title=\"Rivian Automotive, Inc.\">RIVN</a></span>). Shares of the company closed up about 11.2% on increased optimism for the electric vehicle market and following some</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488373216/image_1488373216.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743222-putting-rivian-automotive-stock-latest-surge-in-perspective-reiterate-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 12:55:49"}, {"id": "4743220", "title": "Payoneer Global: The Young Company Is A Strong Candidate For A Growth Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Step of coin stack on top wooden working table with city background and world map,global network business banking concept.\" data-id=\"931538460\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">pookpiik</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With an innovative business model and abilities to cater global online transactions through various channels, Payoneer Global (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PAYO\" title=\"Payoneer Global Inc.\">PAYO</a></span>) generated high mid-teen percentage growth throughout 2024, with an expectation for a significant room for expansion in the following years. Its</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931538460/image_931538460.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743220-payoneer-global-a-young-company-is-a-strong-candidate-for-a-growth-portfolio", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 12:50:25"}, {"id": "4743219", "title": "Mullen Group: An Improving Outlook After A Strong Q3", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/594827553/image_594827553.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Truck driving on remote highway\" data-id=\"594827553\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/594827553/image_594827553.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/594827553/image_594827553.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/594827553/image_594827553.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/594827553/image_594827553.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/594827553/image_594827553.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/594827553/image_594827553.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.see