/s3/uploads/getty_images/1194975140/image_1194975140.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1194975140/image_1194975140.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1194975140/image_1194975140.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1194975140/image_1194975140.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Hiroshi Watanabe/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>The semiconductor memory market is witnessing a few history-altering moments that are sure to change the course of the entire industry. GenAI already did its bit to rock the boat enough to create a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1194975140/image_1194975140.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743216-micron-stock-on-a-mission-to-penetrate-the-hbm-market-buy-it", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 12:38:09"}, {"id": "4743214", "title": "Micron Q1 Preview: Mixed Signals Going Into Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Taking decisions for the future\" data-id=\"638787162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">BrianAJackson</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>Performance Assessment</span></h2> <p>My <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723935-micron-q4-results-didnt-get-me-excited\">last note</a> on Micron (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a></span>) expressed a rather contrarian view as I took a neutral stance amid the bullish cries of analysts from Seeking Alpha, Wall St and even the Quant Ratings. I think my</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638787162/image_638787162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743214-micron-q1-preview-mixed-signals-going-into-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 12:33:11"}, {"id": "4743226", "title": "Planet Labs PBC 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Planet Labs PBC in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106087\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743226-planet-labs-pbc-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 12:23:33"}, {"id": "4743210", "title": "LIT: Buying Lithium At A Bargain", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lithium mine of silver peak\" data-id=\"1392927109\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">simonkr/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I am bullish on the <strong>LIT Global X Lithium &amp; Battery Tech ETF</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LIT\" title=\"Global X Lithium &amp; Battery Tech ETF\">LIT</a></span>) and I have initiated a long position. Although I believe that the broader market may be headed towards an overheated</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392927109/image_1392927109.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743210-lit-buying-lithium-at-a-bargain", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 12:20:56"}, {"id": "4743207", "title": "NIO Is Getting Ready For A Fantastic 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='NIO logo and the Nio\"s user center, NIO House' data-id=\"1271270928\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4032px\" height=\"3024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andy Feng</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Deliveries of EV company <strong>NIO Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NIO\" title=\"NIO Inc.\">NIO</a></span>) </strong>are skyrocketing amid a boost in demand for the company\u2019s new slate of affordable electric vehicles.</p> <p>NIO has started to ship its new Onvo electric vehicles recently, which are met by</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1271270928/image_1271270928.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743207-nio-is-getting-ready-for-a-fantastic-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 12:03:08"}, {"id": "4743205", "title": "Nordic American Tankers: Limited Downside Protection To Weaknesses In The Suezmax Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185275855/image_185275855.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial View of Crude Oil Tanker and Storage Tanks\" data-id=\"185275855\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Crude Oil Tanker &amp; Storage Tanks</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">rgaydos</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Description</h2> <p><a href=\"https://www.nat.bm/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nordic American Tankers</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NAT\" title=\"Nordic American Tankers Limited\">NAT</a></span>) owns and operates a fleet of 20 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suezmax\" rel=\"nofollow\">Suezmax</a> tankers, each capable of lifting 1.0 million barrels of oil, or the equivalent of ~160,000 </p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743205-nordic-american-tankers-limited-downside-protection-to-weaknesses-in-the-suezmax-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 11:51:07"}, {"id": "4743203", "title": "YETI Holdings: Fairly Valued And Positioned For Success", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Large store billboard of Yeti retail in downtown, wide collection of outdoor products ice chests, vacuum-insulated stainless-steel drinkware, camping, hiking, fishing\" data-id=\"1763925921\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">TrongNguyen/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>YETI Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/YETI\" title=\"YETI Holdings, Inc.\">YETI</a></span>) is establishing a durable competitive advantage across online and brick-and-mortar retail channels. Its flagship drinkware products have been a key driver of success in international markets, positioning the company to expand</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1763925921/image_1763925921.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743203-yeti-holdings-fairly-valued-and-positioned-for-success", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 11:43:01"}]}